{"tid":503562,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老Tea Time討論] 呢度有無人飲開中茶/綠茶?","createTime":"2017-12-19T03:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T11:37:17.000Z","uid":76683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f8db5dcd2b1b6cb3281166699d8deb072b016e23","tid":503562,"uid":76683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"之前有巴開過冷泡茶post, 試過兩隻,唔係幾啱飲;<br />\n有無d易上手嘅茶器介紹&amp;價錢中等嘅茶介紹<br />\n利申: 淨係飲過台灣茶(東方美人, 文山包種果d),本人偏好清茶"},{"pid":"f5f3692929127b928d900772fe1357d77fe24724","tid":503562,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"留名 想知邊到買茶葉好"},{"pid":"4fc20aa2a671b981a3f8cff5def38360f64e5e61","tid":503562,"uid":76683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 想知邊到買茶葉好</blockquote><br />\n高手出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食壽司/刺身配咩茶好啊?"},{"pid":"13a37c19b9809fa1ecb47244bb8b9dccb3f0e0ac","tid":503562,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名 想知邊到買茶葉好</blockquote><br />\n高手出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食壽司/刺身配咩茶好啊?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我對茶真唔熟<br />\n同埋我見食壽司好少配茶架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通常都sake<br />\n一係就飲返個度啲抹茶"},{"pid":"e8c1b1673b7ce9af631e4ac027df8f90b8d4c2eb","tid":503562,"uid":155254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"有飲開唔同既茶. 龍井, 鐵觀音用蓋碗沖就可以. 週末時間多就用紫砂壺泡普洱. 佐敦裕華五樓有唔同既茶試. 茶葉水溫茶器水質環境季節時間心境全部都有影響.<br />\n<br />\n龍井好多人都受唔到. 開始簡簡單單用蓋碗沖台灣烏龍都唔錯 (185度水溫 5-7g 茶葉). 第一泡醒茶溫杯唔飲."},{"pid